      <title>墨西哥斥资 27 亿美元扩建港口，无视特朗普威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/mexico-looks-past-trump-trade-threat-with-2-7-billion-manzanillo-port-expansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥并不担心即将上任的特朗普政府的关税威胁，无论其北方邻国和最大贸易伙伴采取什么行动，它都看好全球商品贸易的光明未来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/mexico-looks-past-trump-trade-threat-with-2-7-billion-manzanillo-port-expansion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Nov 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迪拜房地产热潮让买家想方设法抢占地盘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/dubai-real-estate-boom-investors-eying-reits-fractional-ownership-apps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜已逐渐成为全球最热门的房地产市场之一，但其房价却越来越高，买家对此望而却步，这导致人们对房地产投资信托的兴趣再度燃起，许多人转向只需支付 136 美元的部分所有权应用程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/dubai-real-estate-boom-investors-eying-reits-fractional-ownership-apps</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Nov 2024 13:29:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
